title: Reincarnate
info:
Winner of Psycle Compo#4 in January 2004.

---

Readme:
This is my hardcore compo entry. All native plugins, 4 song parts, almost 10 minutes, many many machines and also many many patterns, very few doubly used ones.

have fun!

If your PC is too slow to play it, either render it to wave or use this convenient mp3 link ;)
http://www.lastfuture.de/mp3/ost5/reincarnate.mp3
